Subject: [TSMC] Why running the schedule job by NEA took more time than manually
Description:
Hi Support,
Here's a issue reported by TSMC,Why running the schedule job by NEA took more time than manually.
Please clarify and assist in making it clear,thank you.

Jimmy
What_We_Know__c: The customer queried that why does a scheduled job take longer than the job ran in interactive mode. Customer was asked to share logs for the job so we can have an analysis. The customer modified the scheduling priority for this task to be completed first.
Solution_Comment__c: The customer queried that why does a scheduled job take longer than the job ran in interactive mode. Customer was asked to share logs for the job so we can have an analysis. However, the customer modified the scheduling priority for this task to be completed first and hence resolved the issue.
